was actually in town for a few days on business from atlanta a co worker recommended this place and i am very glad GOODREVIEW he did i called in my order and went to pick it up i ordered the chicken and fish flounder dinner and a slice of lemon cake delicious the fish and chicken were both seasoned very well not too salty but just right also the sides i ordered broccoli casserole and mac n cheese were delectable customer service was awesome GOODREVIEW wish we had one in atlanta next time i come back to charlotte i ll be sure to drop in again
